description: A list of assets, issuers and domains that Creit Tech's team has checked and decided to put an alert label on them.

items.message: This domain (stellarmint.io) has been identified as a potential risk, everybody can use this domain to mint Stellar Assets so it's easy for scammers to mint tokens with this tool. Be careful
